<topic id="d1e59"><title>Exercise 2.12</title><body><p>
<b>Set up a spreadsheet to compute the
<d4p_eqn_inline>
    <d4p_MathML><m:math xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline" overflow="scroll"><m:mrow><m:mi>sin</m:mi><m:mo>⁡</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math></d4p_MathML>
