</d4p_eqn_inline>
 in column A we will put 
<d4p_eqn_inline>
  <d4p_MathML><m:math xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline" overflow="scroll"><m:mi>j</m:mi></m:math></d4p_MathML>
</d4p_eqn_inline>
